display_name: ContractWorkspaceHistory transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 1

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'ContractWorkspace_' || "CW"."DocumentId_InternalId" AS "ContractWorkspace",
    'ContractWorkspaceHistory_' || "CW"."InternalId" AS "ID",
    --'SourcingProject_' ||  "SourcingProject"."DocumentId_InternalId" AS "SourcingProject",
    "CW"."InternalId" AS "InternalId",
    "CW"."Origin" AS "Origin",
    "CW"."IsReportVersion" AS "IsReportVersion",
    cast("CW"."NoticePeriod"  AS int) AS "NoticePeriod", 
    cast("CW"."DefaultingSetBits" AS int) AS "DefaultingSetBits",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."LastModified") AS "LastModified",
    "CW"."AmendmentReason" AS "AmendmentReason",
    --"CW"."ParentDocument" AS "ParentDocument",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "CW"."MatchAtleastOneStatusPerProcessType" AS "MatchAtleastOneStatusPerProcessType",
    "CW"."Status" AS "Status",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."OriginalExpirationDate") AS "OriginalExpirationDate",
    --"CW"."TemplateObject" AS "TemplateObject",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "CW"."Description" AS "Description",
    "CW"."IsForMinervaInterface" AS "IsForMinervaInterface",
    "CW"."ProcessStatus" AS "ProcessStatus",
    "CW"."AmendmentReasonComment" AS "AmendmentReasonComment",
    cast("CW"."NoticeReminderBegin" AS int) AS "NoticeReminderBegin",
    "CW"."PartitionNumber" AS "PartitionNumber",
    --"CW"."Supplier" AS "Supplier",                                              JSON FORMAT
    cast("CW"."DocumentVersion" AS int) AS "DocumentVersion",
    "CW"."IsSubContentPinned" AS "IsSubContentPinned",
    cast("CW"."Rank" AS int) AS "Rank",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."TimeUpdated") AS "TimeUpdated",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."ExpirationDate") AS "ExpirationDate",
    cast("CW"."AdapterFlag" AS int) AS "AdapterFlag",
    "CW"."IsContractRequest" AS "IsContractRequest",
    cast("CW"."PurgeState" AS int) AS "PurgeState",
    cast("CW"."NoticeReminderFrequency" AS int) AS "NoticeReminderFrequency",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."CreateDate") AS "CreateDate",
    cast("CW"."AutoRenewalCount" AS int) AS "AutoRenewalCount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."LastPublishedDate") AS "LastPublishedDate",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("CW"."TimeCreated" AS timestamp)) AS "TimeCreated",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("CW"."HeadersLastModified" AS timestamp)) AS "HeadersLastModified",
    cast("CW"."Version" AS int) AS "Version",
    "CW"."ExpirationTermType" AS "ExpirationTermType",
    "CW"."AgreementPath" AS "AgreementPath",
    "CW"."Active" AS "Active",
    "CW"."ContractType" AS "ContractType",
    --"CW"."Region" AS "Region",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "CW"."HierarchicalType" AS "HierarchicalType",
    "CW"."LockAccessControl" AS "LockAccessControl",
    "CW"."DoNotAllowPublishingContractsWithUnApprovedFactories" AS "ContractsWithUnApprovedFactoriesNotAllow",
    "CW"."HasContentFromDMS" AS "HasContentFromDMS",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."AgreementDate") AS "AgreementDate",
    "CW"."ContractStatus" AS "ContractStatus",
    "CW"."DoNotAllowPublishingContractsWithBlockedFactories" AS "ContractsWithBlockedFactoriesNotAllow",
    "CW"."IsEvergreen" AS "IsEvergreen",
    --"CW"."AffectedParties" AS "AffectedParties",                                              JSON FORMAT
    --"CW"."Commodity" AS "Commodity",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "CW"."isAdhocTaskRestricted" AS "IsAdhocTaskRestricted",
    "CW"."Changed" AS "Changed",
    "CW"."IsComplexSpendWorkspace" AS "IsComplexSpendWorkspace",
    "CW"."TimeZoneID" AS "TimeZoneID",
    cast("CW"."ExpiringReminderFrequency" AS int) AS "ExpiringReminderFrequency",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."NoticeDate") AS "NoticeDate",
    "CW"."IsVersionPinned" AS "IsVersionPinned",
    "CW"."AllowAdhocSpend" AS "AllowAdhocSpend",
    "CW"."AclId" AS "AclId",
    "CW"."Title" AS "Title",
    "CW"."SourceApplicationSite" AS "SourceApplicationSite",
    "CW"."ExpiringReminderBegin" AS "ExpiringReminderBegin",
    "CW"."MaxAutoRenewalsAllowed" AS "MaxAutoRenewalsAllowed",
    "CW"."Alert" AS "Alert",
    "CW"."ParentDocumentVersion" AS "ParentDocumentVersion",
    "CW"."ProcessId" AS "ProcessId",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."EffectiveDate") AS "EffectiveDate",
    "CW"."ProjectAddin_IsTest" AS "ProjectAddinIsTest",
    "CW"."ProjectAddin_Plan_Title_DefaultStringTranslation" AS "ProjectAddinPlanTitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    "CW"."ProjectAddin_Plan_ProcessId" AS "ProjectAddinPlanProcessId",
    "CW"."ProjectAddin_IsSubproject" AS "ProjectAddinIsSubproject",
    "CW"."ParentDocument_InternalId" AS "ParentDocumentInternalId",
    "CW"."TemplateObject_InternalId" AS "TemplateObjectInternalId",
    "CW"."Description_DefaultStringTranslation" AS "DescriptionDefaultStringTranslation",
    "CW"."BusinessSystem_Id" AS "BusinessSystemId",
    "CW"."BusinessSystem_Name" AS "BusinessSystemName",
    cast("CW"."Amount_Amount" AS float) AS "AmountAmount",
    "CW"."Amount_Currency_UniqueName" AS "AmountCurrencyUniqueName",
    cast("CW"."ComplexSpendAvailableAmount_Amount" AS float) AS "ComplexSpendAvailableAmountAmount",
    "CW"."BaseLanguage_UniqueName" AS "BaseLanguageUniqueName",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"CW"."NoteBox_CreateDate") AS "NoteBoxCreateDate",
    "CW"."NoteBox_InternalId" AS "NoteBoxInternalId",
    "CW"."AttrsBlob_TextFlag" AS "AttrsBlobTextFlag",
    "CW"."AttrsBlob_CharSet" AS "AttrsBlobCharSet",
    "CW"."AttrsBlob_Lang" AS "AttrsBlobLang",
    "CW"."Title_DefaultStringTranslation" AS "TitleDefaultStringTranslation",
    "CW"."DefaultScheduleSearchFilter_Required" AS "DefaultScheduleSearchFilterRequired",
    "CW"."DocumentId_InternalId" AS "DocumentIdInternalId"
FROM "ContractWorkspace" AS "CW"
